.PP
FREERDP_WLROOTS_HACK
.RS 4
If defined 0 disables multimonitor detection hack entirely. Set to 1 to force enabled.
.br
By default fall back to detection of sway or other wlroots based compositors by evaluating \fIXDG_SESSION_DESKTOP\fR and \fIXDG_CURRENT_DESKTOP\fR.
.br
.br
Rationale: wlroots based compositors do not expose display information to invisible windows so we have no proper way to query the current monitor layout.
.br
With this hack enabled we fall back and try to determine the resolutions by querying less reliable display resolution and scaling details.
.RE
